\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Kolosi  
\mt2 Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ Towoęž‰ We  
\ip Kolosi amisaęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ Aęž‰sia Maina hen aęž‰na elen. Amisaęž‰n aęž‰noęž‰ Aęž‰fesaęž‰s amisaęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowoęž‰. Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Kolosi saęž‰s aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰doęž‰. Koęž‰sega Foęž‰l e Aęž‰fesaęž‰s aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ saęž‰s nanog dimaęž‰ki Aęž‰sia hen aęž‰na iligaęž‰feloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu noloęž‰ Kolosi amisaęž‰n aęž‰na haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, saęž‰s nanogoęž‰ aęž‰na diaęž‰len.  
\ip Tif amioęž‰ madaliloęž‰ widan kalu noloęž‰ Kolosi saęž‰s us aęž‰na tindaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, tilidabu ililoęž‰woęž‰ noęž‰nolo alitaki, hala widaęž‰lab. Ililoęž‰ hala widaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ tilidabu ililoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ halale alitakiyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ wenamioęž‰ Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widoęž‰. Kelegoęž‰ tambo daęž‰lab wemaęž‰ misaęž‰yoęž‰ Keliso E koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. Keliso imilise eyoęž‰sa nioęž‰ tambo aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰ib, koęž‰loęž‰ ni asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ tog noloęž‰ mada aundoęž‰ma dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Keliso eya ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tambo we e faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Keliso eloęž‰ nanog dimidoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ daęž‰lab we tambo aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ ene diaęž‰ib. Keliso e ni usa aęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale hoęž‰gi taęž‰taki, ene man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰.  
\ip Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, kalu aęž‰laęž‰, Tikikus oęž‰liaęž‰ Onesimus oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ diaęž‰haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Kolosi kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Onesimus weloęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s nowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ Filemonboęž‰woęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Ne Foęž‰l, ne Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ enedoęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Nao Timoti nainoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l.   
\p
\v 2 Nainoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we Godeyaęž‰ ene maliloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Kolosi amisaęž‰n aęž‰namiloęž‰ sab oęž‰moęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l. Gioęž‰ Keliso amioęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰, ene nanogdoęž‰ dimidaęž‰laboęž‰ gi oęž‰m.  
\p Do Gode eyoęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki, dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\s1 Kolosi kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amioęž‰ hendele tilidabu  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1.3 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.15-16\x*Nainoęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ iya Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen.  
\v 4 Mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰senoęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Gililoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gililoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ naęž‰noęž‰ dabu.  
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 1.5-6 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.13, 1Bid 1.4\x*Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ giloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰na tilidabu. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafa koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dimidaliaęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ Hebeneloęž‰ diaęž‰foęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ hendele diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laki asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰sa yasisab. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ gab aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, gili tilidabu oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰ us amioęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰lab. Henfeloęž‰ we tambo amioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowakiyoęž‰, fowoęž‰ modoęž‰ hedaęž‰lab. Gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ tamina daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ asululiab aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, fowoęž‰ gi amioęž‰loęž‰ hedaęž‰i yaęž‰lab.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt Kolo 4.12, File 1.23\x*To nafa aęž‰noęž‰ Ebafelas eyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ widoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ tambo asululi koęž‰loęž‰lab. Ebafelas e ni oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu imilig nowoęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ e alan asuloęž‰. Eyoęž‰ nioęž‰, asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ nanogoęž‰ hendele difoęž‰koęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lab.  
\v 8 Eyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ giya dotaęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ naęž‰nboęž‰woęž‰ malolomeabe.   
\s1 Kolosi kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki, dulugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 1.9 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.16-17\x*Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰len gililoęž‰ man nafa dimidab aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dabuloęž‰ aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, nainoęž‰ gioęž‰ asulaki, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ towoęž‰ safoęž‰koęž‰ yaęž‰loęž‰l. Mama Maliloęž‰ eyoęž‰ asulumaęž‰noęž‰ nafayoęž‰ gimoęž‰ dimiab amioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ gi amioęž‰ ililitaęž‰gaęž‰ asululimaęž‰ki dulugu saęž‰laęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 10 Aęž‰laęž‰gab amioęž‰ gioęž‰ Alan eloęž‰ asulab oęž‰leau kudu haęž‰naęž‰liki, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo gililoęž‰ dimidab amioęž‰, e sagalemaęž‰ki dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰ giliyoęž‰ man nafa dimidaki, fowoęž‰ modoęž‰ hedaęž‰melaęž‰ib, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ fanda asululiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gi amioęž‰ asulufoęž‰koęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 1.11-12 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.19, 3.16\x*\x - \xo 1.11-12 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.11,18\x*Godeyaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ maliloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ halale alitakiyoęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ yab aęž‰noęž‰ haęž‰sa iliki halale diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, moęž‰taęž‰taki haęž‰naęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, nainoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰gab amioęž‰ gioęž‰ sagalaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ Domoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ to saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li daęž‰lab. Eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafale koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale enedoęž‰lemaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ dimidaefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰ dimaęž‰ki ilili alifaęž‰. Kalukaęž‰isale Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰le aęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len nafale us aęž‰na aęž‰lab.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1.13 \xt Luk 22.53, Aęž‰fe 2.2\x*Nioęž‰ sololi halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga aęž‰labiki, Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasiliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ene haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ disaęž‰ Soęž‰wa aęž‰maęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰liki, eloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰na meleaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1.14 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.7\x*Soęž‰wa aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, nioęž‰ sili alitaki, nili mogagoęž‰woęž‰ tambo halaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.   
\s1 Keliso e mada waęž‰laęž‰bdeyoęž‰ E  
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 1.15 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.18, 2Kol 4.4\x*Nioęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰sega Yaęž‰su Keliso e Gode enen misidoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wa waęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ E koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ we tambo amioęž‰, E misaęž‰ iliki boęž‰foęž‰lab.  
\v 16 Soęž‰wa aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰. Hebene kelegoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nililoęž‰ boęž‰doęž‰l weloęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nililoęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰doęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰, mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, enoęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1.17 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.1, 8.58\x*Kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ oęž‰semoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, E koęž‰le elen. Kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ ene digi taęž‰li dofoęž‰likiyoęž‰, egoęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1.18 \xt Ilig 26.23, Aęž‰fe 1.22-23, Kala 1.5\x*Kalukaęž‰isale e amiloęž‰ kudoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ene saęž‰s dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ iyoęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰le dowaki, ili misaęž‰yoęž‰ E koęž‰loęž‰lab. Doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ E. E iwaluloęž‰ taminde domaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, sowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ daidoęž‰ amiloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasioęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ E.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1.19 \xt Kolo 2.9\x*Godeyaęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ ene man oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, e amiloęž‰ ilili alifoęž‰lab oęž‰leaumboęž‰, ene Soęž‰wa e amioęž‰loęž‰ tambo ilili alifomaęž‰kiyoęž‰ sagalaęž‰li taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1.20 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.10\x*Gode eyoęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Hebene kelegoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo e oęž‰liaęž‰ ege domaęž‰ki asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ i malan amiloęž‰ tuloęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ni oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na disaęž‰. \fig Godeyaęž‰ ene Soęž‰wa eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.|alt="Creation, Adam, Eve" src="DY01001_gr.tif" size="col" copy="by Carolyn Dyk (SIL)" ref="1.15-16" \fig*   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 1.21 \xt Lom 5.10, Aęž‰fe 2.12\x*Moęž‰luwoęž‰ giliyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰le dimidaęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis diaęž‰liki, alobanalaęž‰ elen.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1.22 \xt Lom 5.10, Aęž‰fe 5.27\x*Koęž‰sega Yaęž‰su Keliso sowoęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰ege domaęž‰ki dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ goęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ tililiaęž‰gaęž‰ ene siwaęž‰la kagayalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ maliloęž‰ dowaki, mogagoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ hala dimidan oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mada aundoęž‰ma elena baęž‰baęž‰ib.  
\v 23 Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰ koęž‰sega gini tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ aikoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ mada halale geloęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ dofoęž‰lubi. Gioęž‰ to nafa hoęž‰gi daęž‰dakiyoęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰nigoęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ sulu haęž‰nabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, taęž‰li dofoęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lubi. To nafa aęž‰noęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambomoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰li ane koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ dabu. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Foęž‰l ne to aęž‰maęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Kolosi saęž‰s aęž‰noęž‰ asufaęž‰  
\p
\v 24 Oęž‰goęž‰ gi asuwaęž‰takiloęž‰ nagaloęž‰ dioęž‰l we ne sagaloęž‰l. Moęž‰woęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ nagaloęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰ semoęž‰ ilili alifaęž‰. Saęž‰soęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰noęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, nagaloęž‰ heb oęž‰dowab aęž‰noęž‰ ni doęž‰moęž‰ wemaęž‰ dioęž‰l.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1.25 \xt Aęž‰fe 3.2,7-8\x*Gode eyoęž‰ ne saęž‰s usa nanog diaki, gi asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki ene halaidoęž‰waęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰. Gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ tambo daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asululimaęž‰kiyoęž‰, ne aęž‰na taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 1.26 \xt Lom 16.25-26, Aęž‰fe 3.5,9\x*Moęž‰luwoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰le delen koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ taęž‰i mioęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ tambo moęž‰asuloęž‰. Koęž‰sega oęž‰goęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale enedoęž‰smaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰.  
\v 27 Gode eyoęž‰ to woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰ widalikiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nafale to us amiloęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Yu kalukaęž‰isalema imoęž‰woęž‰ kalaba walamaęž‰noęž‰ asulabi widoęž‰. To woęž‰noęž‰le delen aęž‰noęž‰ we. Yaęž‰su Keliso e gi usa aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰ silikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, tambo hendele diaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 28 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso e koęž‰loęž‰ fanda widaęž‰loęž‰l. Niliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ tambo, Kelisowa dowaki tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰likiyoęž‰, Godeloęž‰wa tililiaęž‰ miaęž‰noęž‰ asulab koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafale kudu haęž‰naki, imoęž‰woęž‰ hagugoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰loęž‰, towoęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ widaęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 1.29 \xt Aęž‰fe 3.7,20, Fili 4.13\x*Aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ nemoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ nanog halaidoęž‰ we disugulaki dimidaęž‰loęž‰l.   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Niyoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale misiloęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰faęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰lakiyoęž‰, hogoęž‰ nanog diaęž‰loęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki asulab. Kalukaęž‰isale neloęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰doęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale Laodisia hen amiloęž‰ sab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale ne misiloęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen.  
\v 2 Nanog niloęž‰ dimidoęž‰l wemaęž‰yoęž‰, tilidabu gililoęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki goęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ tambo gegeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laki, ua gasa domaęž‰ki goęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰gabikiyoęž‰ gioęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ delen aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ dinafa fanda asululialikiyoęž‰, gili tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki asuloęž‰l. To woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ delen aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso we.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2.3 \xt 1Kol 1.24,30\x*Asuloęž‰ nafale oęž‰liaęž‰ asulumaęž‰noęž‰ nafa oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo Keliso amioęž‰, waęž‰lifoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2.4 \xt Lom 16.18\x*Kalu nomaęž‰yoęž‰ to nafa koęž‰li nowoęž‰ gioęž‰ dikili saęž‰lab amioęž‰ tili daęž‰dabenaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ to we gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na soęž‰loęž‰l  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2.5 \xt 1Kol 5.3\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ ne gi oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰dofoęž‰loęž‰l koęž‰sega, asuloęž‰ niloęž‰woęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ ua iliki, gioęž‰ Keliso amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dakiloęž‰ halale kagayab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰, gegeleloęž‰ ege dowab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, ne asulaki sagalaęž‰liki soęž‰l.   
\s1 Kaluwaęž‰ towoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naki, Yaęž‰su amioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰le diaęž‰ib  
\p
\v 6 Giliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ gili Alande domaęž‰kiloęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gioęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo e oęž‰liaęž‰ iliki haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2.7 \xt Aęž‰fe 3.17\x*Gioęž‰ i tef koęž‰loęž‰ hen amiloęž‰ tihaęž‰nan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, E amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰kudaki bowoęž‰ tinaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ a koęž‰loęž‰ aikoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ waęž‰l amiloęž‰ dian oęž‰leaumboęž‰ gili tilidabuwoęž‰ e waęž‰la diaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, nililoęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰ gili tilidabuwoęž‰ halale anayakiyoęž‰, sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ gi amioęž‰ waęž‰litakiyoęž‰ ala handalomaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 8 Gioęž‰ dinafa dowaęž‰bi. Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ dikili saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, madali to koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ walamaęž‰ib. To aęž‰noęž‰ emaęž‰muwaęž‰ asuloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowakiyoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ wemaęž‰ man delen aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakigab. Ililoęž‰ to widab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ dibolo amiloęž‰ toęž‰loloęž‰woęž‰ aumaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰nabenaęž‰ki dinafa dowaęž‰bi. To aęž‰noęž‰ Keliso eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowab.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2.9 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.14,16\x*Keliso e kalu dofoęž‰labi, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo Gode amiloęž‰ waęž‰lifoęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e amioęž‰loęž‰ waęž‰lifoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2.10 \xt Aęž‰fe 1.21-22\x*Gioęž‰ Yaęž‰su eya kudufoęž‰labikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ gi amioęž‰ tambo ilili alifaęž‰. Keliso e, mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ misaęž‰yoęž‰ E koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2.11 \xt Lom 2.29\x*Gioęž‰ eya kudabiki, eyoęž‰ gili doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ aęž‰na hege gede alifaęž‰. Eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰f hege gedean oęž‰mba. Keliso eyoęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulakiloęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len man aęž‰noęž‰, gioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki sili alifaęž‰. Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedean man hendeleyoęž‰ oęž‰m.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2.12 \xt Lom 6.4\x*Gioęž‰ hoęž‰n amiloęž‰ toęž‰lolab aęž‰namioęž‰, Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ hen daidoęž‰wa difaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰suloęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ Gode aęž‰maęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, gioęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2.13 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.1,4-5\x*Tamin amioęž‰ gili doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulakiloęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len man aęž‰noęž‰ semoęž‰ dilaęž‰ amioęž‰, gioęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰liki sowoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ elen. Koęž‰sega oęž‰g aęž‰namioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nili mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ tambo halaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alitakiyoęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2.14 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.14-16, 1Bid 2.24\x*Ele difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ moęž‰walilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, nililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba diaęž‰taki, nioęž‰ mewaęž‰l haęž‰g aęž‰na elen. Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ mewaęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ i malana alu alitaki tambo dilaęž‰.  
\v 15 I malan aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ tambo tiniakiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ sendelomaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰.   
\s1 Nioęž‰ Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ henfeloęž‰waęž‰ eleyoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰niki  
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 2.16 \xt Lom 14.1-13\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ maęž‰n maęž‰noęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰n maęž‰noęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰len alan amiloęž‰ gulugululan aęž‰namidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰, ele hoęž‰gi amiloęž‰ gulugululan aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Haęž‰foęž‰loęž‰ Dowan hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ ele diaęž‰tab aęž‰namioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰alobanamaęž‰ki dowaęž‰bi.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2.17 \xt Hibu 8.5\x*Ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tif amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ mama dowan oęž‰ngoęž‰ dedaki dimidoęž‰. Koęž‰sega hendele aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso e koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 18 Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ giloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib, â€śGioęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalumoęž‰ gulugululaki wabulumaâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib, â€śNiyoęž‰ Godeya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ hoęž‰le baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ to niloęž‰ widoęž‰l we mada dinafa daęž‰daęž‰bi,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega giliyoęž‰ kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰ sanamaęž‰kiyoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰soęž‰bo. Kalu i oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ inidoęž‰ asuloęž‰wa ilikiyoęž‰, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ madali kailakigab.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 2.19 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.21, 4.16\x*Kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ misaęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ moęž‰kudoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. Nili misaęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso E. Nili doęž‰moęž‰ amioęž‰ moma oęž‰liaęž‰ kagoman oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo kudu alifeloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nili misaęž‰ aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nili doęž‰moęž‰ we halaidoęž‰woęž‰ dimiab amioęž‰ tambo anamaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰sen.   
\p
\v 20 \x - \xo 2.20 \xt Gala 4.3,9, 1Tim 4.3\x*Gioęž‰ Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ sowabikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man wemaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki sili alifaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man wemaęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰ oęž‰aęž‰lab oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowakiloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab ko moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰?  
\v 21 Henfeloęž‰ wemaęž‰ eleyoęž‰ we. Kelegoęž‰ we golaęž‰soęž‰bo! Aęž‰noęž‰ naęž‰soęž‰bo! Kelegoęž‰ nowoęž‰ taęž‰liaęž‰soęž‰bo!  
\v 22 \x - \xo 2.22 \xt Madi 15.9\x*Ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ boęž‰eloęž‰ mogailaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namidaęž‰ saęž‰laki difaęž‰. Ele oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ kaluwa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.  
\v 23 Ele oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ â€śWe nafa, hendele asuwaęž‰faęž‰nigaboęž‰loęž‰bâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰. Kalukaęž‰isale eleloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, eleyoęž‰ tambo mada dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰niki aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰sen. Ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ madali waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰ndaki, eleyoęž‰ aęž‰na difaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ini doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, eleyoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dilaęž‰. Koęž‰sega ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nili mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ mada moęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰lab.   
\c 3  
\s1 Man moęž‰luwoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hoęž‰gile dima  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3.1 \xt Mak 12.36, 16.19, Aęž‰fe 1.20\x*Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ Keliso e oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ Hebene halomiloęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ mada alan asulaęž‰lubi. Iwalu halonamioęž‰ Keliso e misaęž‰ siliki, Godeyaęž‰ ene dagi ililiba sab.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3.2 \xt Madi 6.33\x*Henfeloęž‰ wenamiloęž‰ daęž‰lab kelegoęž‰ we moęž‰asulaki, iwaluloęž‰ daęž‰lab kelegoęž‰ halo koęž‰loęž‰ mada asulufoęž‰lubi.  
\v 3 Moęž‰woęž‰ gioęž‰ sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gi melaęž‰noęž‰le aęž‰noęž‰ Kelisowa woęž‰noęž‰le diaęž‰foęž‰liki, Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 4 Keliso e gili melaęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ E koęž‰loęž‰, E kalaba faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ e oęž‰liaęž‰ ene hoęž‰len maliloęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ kalaba faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 3.5 \xt Lom 6.6,11, Aęž‰fe 4.19, 5.3-6\x*Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gililoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ sana sowaęž‰bi. Man aęž‰noęž‰ we. Uwoęž‰ dian manoęž‰, heyoęž‰ manoęž‰, doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan manoęž‰, man mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulan manoęž‰, meselan manoęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰m. Meselan man aęž‰noęž‰ madali Godemoęž‰loęž‰ gulugululan oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 6 Man dimidan aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰woęž‰ timaęž‰nigab.  
\v 7 Tamin amioęž‰ gili melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na elen koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ dimidafoęž‰koęž‰ dowaęž‰len.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3.8 \xt Aęž‰fe 4.25-29, 5.4\x*Aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰len koęž‰sega, oęž‰goęž‰ giliyoęž‰ man we oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ tambo dilaęž‰bi. Gadian manoęž‰, kulufaęž‰yan manoęž‰, nowoęž‰mboęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰bean manoęž‰, sadaęž‰danoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ waęž‰saęž‰le saęž‰lanoęž‰, tambo kataęž‰taęž‰bi.  
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 3.9-10 \xt Aęž‰fe 4.22,24,25\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ giliyoęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ madaliyoęž‰ dikili saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ gili mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ asulaęž‰sen man aęž‰noęž‰ tambo dugulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, man hoęž‰gile aęž‰noęž‰ gi amioęž‰ kalifaęž‰. Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ hoęž‰gi kalukaęž‰isale faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ e mada asulufoęž‰liki, enen misidoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ki, eyoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ dimifoęž‰koęž‰ aęž‰lab.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3.11 \xt Gala 3.28\x*Keliso eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ hoęž‰gile faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ tambo imiloęž‰ dowab. Yuda kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ Gilig kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ us amioęž‰ eleyoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ doęž‰goęž‰foęž‰ hege gedeoęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ moęž‰hege gedeoęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰naęž‰ kaluwaęž‰le, to koęž‰liloęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰lan kaluwaęž‰le, madaliloęž‰ nanog dian kaluwaęž‰le, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰le, iyoęž‰ tambo imiloęž‰ dowab. Koęž‰sega alan kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso e koęž‰m, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ e ni usa tambo aęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt 1Bid 2.9\x*Gode eyoęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gioęž‰ maliloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale dowabiki, enoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ manoęž‰ we oęž‰ngoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi. Nofolanoęž‰, nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ man nafa dimidanoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n ge haęž‰ga dowanoęž‰, no oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰sa dowanoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ boęž‰eboęž‰ moęž‰iligan manoęž‰, gioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ tambo kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3.13 \xt Aęž‰fe 4.2,32\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰beaki, kalu nomaęž‰loęž‰ gemoęž‰loęž‰ hala dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰lubi. Alan Keliso eyoęž‰ gili mogagoęž‰woęž‰ halaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, giliyoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ halaki gaęž‰lilaęž‰bi.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3.14 \xt Lom 13.8-10\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰b kelegoęž‰woęž‰ we. Giliyoęž‰ kalu nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lubi. Man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ua kegene kudu alitaki, asuloęž‰ imilise domaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰sen.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3.15 \xt 1Kol 12.27, Aęž‰fe 4.4, Fili 4.7\x*Gioęž‰ tambo Kelisowaęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ heb koęž‰loęž‰, gegeleboęž‰ haęž‰sa domaęž‰ki Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ aęž‰na hoęž‰idoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ ene haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ tambo boęž‰foęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰lubi.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3.16 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.19\x*Kelisowaęž‰ ene to aęž‰noęž‰ gili asuloęž‰ usa amioęž‰ ililitaęž‰gaęž‰ domaęž‰ki taęž‰foma. Gioęž‰ nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ widaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ digalaęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ Godemoęž‰ sagalakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ gisaloęž‰ bugoęž‰ amiloęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, gulugululakiloęž‰ gisaloęž‰ moęž‰lan aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰laęž‰lubi.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3.17 \xt 1Kol 10.31, Aęž‰fe 5.20\x*Gili megoęž‰faęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰loęž‰, nanog dimidakiyoęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ giloęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo, Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya dimidaęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ene wiya ilikiyoęž‰, Do Godemoęž‰woęž‰ sagalaki, mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰lubi.   
\s1 Kalukaęž‰isale no oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ ege domaęž‰noęž‰ manoęž‰ we  
\p
\v 18 \x - \xo 3.18 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.22\x*Ga indoęž‰ giliyoęž‰, ge kaluwaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰bi. Kelisowaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amiloęž‰ man nafa koęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m.   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 3.19 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.25\x*Kalu galoęž‰ di giliyoęž‰, gaęž‰ gayoęž‰ alan asulaki, haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi. Gaęž‰ ga oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰sa dowaki dibodaęž‰soęž‰bo.   
\p
\v 20 \x - \xo 3.20 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.1\x*Soęž‰wale giliyoęž‰ goęž‰l diaęž‰ goęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ towoęž‰ dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Alanoęž‰ sagale alifaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 3.21 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.4\x*Iya i giliyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰ soęž‰wagalinoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ dowabenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ moęž‰bemaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo.   
\p
\v 22 \x - \xo 3.22 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.5-8\x*Madali nanog dian kalu giliyoęž‰ geloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ to saęž‰laboęž‰ tambo dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Giliyoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu eyoęž‰ geloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, e sagale alifaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰ nanog dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega eloęž‰malamioęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ Gode Alanoęž‰ tagilaki haęž‰ga dowakiyoęž‰, ge nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ diaęž‰lubi.  
\v 23 Nanogoęž‰ tambo giliyoęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ diaki dimidaęž‰lubi. Giyoęž‰ ne henfeloęž‰ kaluwaęž‰ nanog dimidoęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰asulaki, Alan Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene nanog dioęž‰l aęž‰laęž‰asulaki diaęž‰bi.  
\v 24 Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuloęž‰, tif amioęž‰ Alan eyoęž‰ waęž‰l dimiakiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ gemoęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib. Gioęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ ene nanog dimidaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, gi misaęž‰ kalu hendeleyoęž‰ e koęž‰m.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 3.25 \xt Lom 2.11\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ ene mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰ib. Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambomoęž‰woęž‰ manoęž‰ imiloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka alobaęž‰daęž‰sen.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 4.1 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.9\x*Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu aęž‰maęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu gioęž‰, geloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ hendeleyoęž‰ Hebene aęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰asulakiyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n nanog dian kalu aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa boęž‰foęž‰liki, imoęž‰woęž‰ man digaloęž‰le dimidaęž‰lubi.   
\s1 Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, manoęž‰ digaloęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi  
\p
\v 2 \x - \xo 4.2 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.18, Fili 4.6\x*Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰loęž‰ to saęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ halale kudu haęž‰naki dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, gili asuloęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beoęž‰loęž‰ma iliki, sagalaki dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt Lom 15.30, Aęž‰fe 6.19\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Niliyoęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ ene to tamin amiloęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰ kalab amiloęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ togoęž‰ kolaefomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰baęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beakiyoęž‰ iliyoęž‰ ne dibolo wena toęž‰loloęž‰.  
\v 4 To hendele daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ fanda samaęž‰ki Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4.5 \xt Aęž‰fe 5.15-16\x*Giyoęž‰ haęž‰laęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ dowakiyoęž‰, asuloęž‰ gililoęž‰woęž‰ nafale asulaki, manoęž‰ digaloęž‰le dimidaęž‰bi. Giliyoęž‰ kalu nolboęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ man walamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo dimidaliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰na widaęž‰lubi.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4.6 \xt Aęž‰fe 4.29, 1Bid 3.15\x*Giliyoęž‰ kalu nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰foęž‰liki towoęž‰ aęž‰na saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ sagalaęž‰likiloęž‰ daęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, giloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ to saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ nafale daęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰li saęž‰maęž‰ib.   
\s1 Sagaloęž‰ to sioęž‰  
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 4.7 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.21\x*Niyoęž‰ Tikikus e giloęž‰wa iligaęž‰toęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ ne amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ tambo malolomeaęž‰ib. Niliyoęž‰ nao e mada alan asuloęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ e negele nanogoęž‰ imilika diaki, Alanaęž‰ ene nanogoęž‰ nafale diaęž‰sen.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4.8 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.22\x*E giloęž‰wa hamanaęž‰kiloęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Eyoęž‰ gili tilidabuwoęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ saboęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki aęž‰na iligaęž‰toęž‰l.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 4.9 \xt File 1.10-12\x*Niyoęž‰ Onesimus e Tikikus oęž‰liaęž‰ giloęž‰wa iligaęž‰toęž‰l. Onesimus e gi oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ amisaęž‰noęž‰ imilise koęž‰loęž‰, e Keliso amioęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, negeleloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ e. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰ wemaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ wiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰woęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ tambo malolomeaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 4.10 \xt Ilig 12.12, 13.13, 15.37-39, 2Tim 4.11\x*Alistakus e ne oęž‰liaęž‰ dibolowa siliki, eyoęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Banabasaęž‰ enesoęž‰g Mak eyoęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab. E giloęž‰ amioęž‰ yalega, niloęž‰ to gimoęž‰loęž‰ sagaęž‰foęž‰ oęž‰leau dimidaki, e dinafa sagalaęž‰liki tilidowaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 11 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ Yaęž‰su, ene wi nowoęž‰ Yastus, eyoęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab. Ne oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene nanogdoęž‰ diaęž‰sen kalu us wenamioęž‰, kalu otalen aęž‰noęž‰, Yu kalu koęž‰loęž‰, Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ i oęž‰m. Iliyoęž‰ ne asuwaęž‰taki, halale alitaęž‰sen.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4.12 \xt Kolo 1.7, File 1.23-24\x*Giasi kalu nowoęž‰ Ebafelas eyoęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab. Gioęž‰ Gode eloęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naki, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo fandaliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ digaloęž‰le iliki, tilidabuwoęž‰ halaidoęž‰le domaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Ebafelas eyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gioęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lab.  
\v 13 Eyoęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale Laodisia oęž‰liaęž‰ Hialabolis amisaęž‰n aęž‰namiloęž‰ sab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰likiyoęž‰, nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab. Aęž‰noęž‰ ne baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 14 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Demas oęž‰liaęž‰, mulumuloęž‰loęž‰ mean kalu, nili mili Luk e oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab.  
\v 15 Giliyoęž‰ nao i Laodisialoęž‰ sab imoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tabekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰biyoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ga Nifa oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, Keliso kalukaęž‰isale e ayamiloęž‰ kegeaęž‰sen oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ sagaęž‰tabekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰biyoęž‰.   
\p
\v 16 Giliyoęž‰ ni moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰l koęž‰ agelaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Laodisia saęž‰s oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ agelemaęž‰ki iligaęž‰taęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ Laodisialoęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ agelaęž‰biyoęž‰.   
\p
